    "updated": "Last updated: June 2025",
    "terms1Title": "1. Acceptance of Terms",
    "terms1Text": "By accessing the UnivVibes platform, you agree to be bound by these terms of service. If you do not agree with these terms, please do not use our services.",
    "terms2Title": "2. Description of Service",
    "terms2Text": "UnivVibes is a student event discovery and management platform. It allows users to discover events, organizers to create and promote their events, and facilitates online ticketing.",
    "terms3Title": "3. User Accounts",
    "terms3Text": "You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your account and password. You must provide accurate and up-to-date information when registering. UnivVibes reserves the right to suspend any account in case of violation of these terms.",
    "terms4Title": "4. Organizers and Events",
    "terms4Text": "Organizers are solely responsible for the content and legality of their events. UnivVibes acts as a technical intermediary and cannot be held responsible for events published on the platform.",
    "terms5Title": "5. Ticketing and Payments",
    "terms5Text": "Transactions are secured via our payment partners. UnivVibes deducts a commission on ticket sales, according to the applicable rates. Refunds are handled directly by the organizers.",
    "privacy1Title": "1. Data Collected",
    "privacy1Text": "We collect information you provide during registration: name, email, university, phone number. We also collect usage data (pages visited, events viewed) to improve our services.",
    "privacy2Title": "2. Use of Data",
    "privacy2Text": "Your data is used to: provide our services, personalize your experience, send relevant notifications, and improve our platform. We never sell your personal data.",
    "privacy3Title": "3. Data Protection",
    "privacy3Text": "We implement technical and organizational security measures to protect your data from unauthorized access, modification, or destruction.",
    "privacy4Title": "4. Your Rights",
    "privacy4Text": "In accordance with regulations, you have the right to access, rectify, and delete your data. To exercise these rights, contact us at privacy@univibes.com.",
    "cookies1Title": "1. What is a Cookie?",
    "cookies1Text": "A cookie is a small text file stored on your device when you visit a website. It enables the site to remember your preferences and improve your browsing experience.",
    "cookies2Title": "2. Cookies Used",
    "cookies2Text": "We use essential cookies for platform functionality (authentication, session) and analytics cookies (to understand how you use the site). We do not use third-party advertising cookies.",
    "cookies3Title": "3. Managing Cookies",
    "cookies3Text": "You can configure your browser to refuse cookies. However, some platform features may not function properly without them."
  },
